dataList.name: Selfie Camera: Filters & Stickers Photo Editor

dataList.appIntro:
Selfie Camera is a great all-in-one photo maker and editor app with photo editor, amazing filter effects, collage photo maker, PIP cam and fun stickers functions together. It’s one of the best photo editor & beauty selfie camera app.
Why Choose Selfie Camera
▲Real-Time Filters
▲Makeup for Beauty
▲Double Exposure
▲Mirror Effects
▲Animal Face Stickers
▲Hairstyle & Eye Color Editor
▲Photo Collage Frames 
▲PIP Camera
▲Pro Editing Tools
====== Feature Highlights ======
【Pro Editing】
This photo editor app offers comprehensive selfie editor tools for you to create amazing photos. Easily become a photo editing master!
* Filter and Sticker
* Double Exposure and Mirror Effect
* Image Blur, Crop, Rotate
* Photo Frame and Texture
* More: set sharpness, temperature, tint, exposure, contrast, vibrance, saturation, shadow & vignette
【Tons of Unique Stickers】
* Makeup – Lips, Eyelash, Eyebrow Makeover
* Abs - Get six-pack abs in one tap
* Tattoo - Get cool and dangerous
* Hairstyle - Long or short? Straight or curly? Try them all in selfie editor.
* Eye Color Editor - You can change your eyes color easily in different colors like!
【Photo Filters and Effects】
Bring magic into your photos! Over 100 classic photo filters to make you a master photographer! Easy to choose from amazing selfie filters and stylize your pics with art filters, previewing favorite filter effect instantly. 
Live filters include Magic Skin/Sky/Color, Mirror, Double Exposure, Analog Film, HDR, Storm, Starry Night, B&W, Sketch, etc.
【Beauty Selfie】
Say goodbye to fake faces and start taking perfect selfies that makes your pictures more natural and beautiful!
- Real-time beauty filters for selfie
- Stylize your pictures with professional beauty selfie filters
- Apply vignette blur effects to enhance candy selfie
【Collage】 
Build with collage feature, this selfie photo editor helps you combine multiple photos with stylish photo collage, collage maker. 
Besides, this great photo editor app supports mirror image, image rotation, draw and add text.
【PIP Camera】
For photo collage with poster effects, try our pic-in-pic frame collage maker - PIP camera. It allows you to combine blurred photos in glass, camera, mirror and more to get pic-in-pic effects. Many poster camera templates are offered.
